Hotel Management System & Hotel Reservation System

Actors:-
- User
- Admin
- Hotel Admin
- System

Story points for MVP:-
- User can register
- User can search hotels\villas\residency etc and filter them on the basis of room size , price ,city, luxury etc.
- User can make multiple reservations at scheduled times
- User can cancel complete or part of a reservation
- Hotel Admin can make/modify/cancel reservations on the behalf of user

Advanced Story Points:-
- user can pay
- User will get the notification for cancellation, booking
- Admin can add/remove/modify hotels in the itinerary
- User can order food/beverages/cab etc.
